b'Features'
b'The Sport & Fitness Center is the hub of recreational activity on the west campus.\xc2\xa0 Located in the middle of the Illinois Medical District and adjacent to the UIC Student Center West, the facility has recently undergone a $10 million dollar renovation.\xc2\xa0 The Sport & Fitness Center is open to UIC students, faculty, staff and University of Illinois Alumni Association members. Employees of health care facilities located in the Illinois Medical District are also eligible for membership.'
